### è¿æ¥åŸºç±» BaseConnection

```python
from pydbpool.base import BaseConnection
from pydbpool.dbpool import DBPool


# å®ç°è‡ªå·±çš„è¿æ¥ç±»
class YourselfConnection(BaseConnection):
    pass


